<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink355">
<l>tiruntiḻai yarivai niṉṉala muḷḷi yaruñceyaṟ poruṭpiṇi peruntiru vuṟukeṉac</l>
<l>collātu peyartan tēṉē palpoṟic</l>
<l>ciṟukaṇ yāṉai tiritaru</l>
<l>neṟivilaṅ katara kāṉat tāṉē</l>
      </lg>
     <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>O woman in perfect jewels! </l>
<l>Thinking of your beauty, I returned without saying:  </l>
<l>“May great prosperity happen, bringing wealth, [obtained] with rare deeds!” </l>
<l>from the jungle, where paths are crossed </l>
<l>by roaming elephants with many spots and small eyes roam. </l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
